# Test-to-spec traceability ([DALC-VER-005])

If you edit a **SHALL** in `openspec/specs/*/spec.md`: put **`[DALC-REQ-…]`** or **`[DALC-VER-…]`** on the **same line** as **`### Requirement:`**; follow **`docs/adrs/0003-spec-test-traceability.md`**; update **`docs/spec-test-traceability.md`**. For pytest, prefer matrix evidence **`path.py::test_function`** and put the ID in **that function’s** docstring; for Helm unittest use **`#` comments**. **Waivers** require maintainer **GitHub username** + **reason** in the matrix—**no drive-by waiver edits**. Run **`python3 scripts/check_spec_traceability.py`**.
